  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nDespite `--JsonRpc.MaxLoggedRequestParametersCharacters=20`, engine API calls are logged in full, e.g.\r\n\r\n```\r\nexecution_1             | 2022-04-06 13:01:27.1801|Sending JSON RPC response: {\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"result\":{\"status\":\"SYNCING\",\"latestValidHash\":null,\"validationError\":null},\"id\":1}\r\nexecution_1             | 2022-04-06 13:01:27.1801|  ID 1, engine_newPayloadV1({\r\nexecution_1             |   \"baseFeePerGas\": \"0x7\",\r\nexecution_1             |   \"blockHash\": \"0x9a836a5fee21bb0782167a9779a503d9af98c75ce4f096ddc753fb4d998c58c1\",\r\nexecution_1             |   \"blockNumber\": \"0x14650\",\r\nexecution_1             |   \"extraData\": \"0x\",\r\nexecution_1             |   \"feeRecipient\": \"0xf97e180c050e5ab072211ad2c213eb5aee4df134\",\r\nexecution_1             |   \"gasLimit\": \"0x7a1200\",\r\nexecution_1             |   \"gasUsed\": \"0x0\",\r\nexecution_1             |   \"logsBloom\": \"\",\r\nexecution_1             |   \"parentHash\": \"0x10abdce9ae67e71a7802be1388f0cd6a552e18f0c3bcc3807b1a92bf43425451\",\r\nexecution_1             |   \"prevRandao\": \"0xf22e58642aa73d3ddf5cb0c4516d4b5cca9cfc78c3ea743d37aa2cb7cfeaef70\",\r\nexecution_1             |   \"receiptsRoot\": \"0x56e81f171bcc55a6ff8345e692c0f86e5b48e01b996cadc001622fb5e363b421\",\r\nexecution_1             |   \"stateRoot\": \"0x2a83cdf4e7782d7f8bd656bca10ee00fc2b094512188658ab85918d650432717\",\r\nexecution_1             |   \"timestamp\": \"0x62366400\",\r\nexecution_1             |   \"transactions\": []\r\nexecution_1             | }) handled in 0.4114ms\r\n```\r\n\r\nEngine RPC calls are via 8551, configured as `--JsonRpc.AdditionalRpcUrls=http://0.0.0.0:8551|http;wss|engine;eth;net;web3;subscribe`\r\n",
